text: Finally, if a commentator on television, a politician or a corporate executive said what @realdontaldtrump did last night in the Ingraham interview they would be immediately fired. Enjoy the day, be safe.

This interview last night between @realdonaldtrump and Laura Ingraham is so retrograde- that I had to post it. In it, Trump equates the value of an unarmed black man being shot with missing a 3 foot golf putt. Even Ingraham was puzzled and had to stop him and hold him back.

The interview is so racist. Trump can't control the eruptions of his racism. He doesn't even talk in code anymore. Whether you are a Republican or Democrat - this shouldnt be tolerable to anyone. I am embarrassed for our country.

His unhinged racist tropes are full of hate and out of the 18th century, not even the 1950s. This is who Trump is, its not latent, its overt. @jimcramer @tomkeene @ScottWapnerCNBC @riskreversal I have had enough, this might be my last post on @realdonaldtrump
This sort of talk and philosophy is unhealthy for our country. I fear its implications. @threadreaderapp unroll
